article.description: — De’Monte Buckingham tied his career high with 28 points as UNC Greensboro narrowly defeated North Carolina A&T 57-53 on Tuesday night in the season opener.
article.headline: Buckingham carries UNC Greensboro over NC A&T 57-53
article.linkText: Buckingham carries UNC Greensboro over NC A&T 57-53
article.story: GREENSBORO, N.C. -- — De’Monte Buckingham tied his career high with 28 points as UNC Greensboro narrowly defeated North Carolina A&T 57-53 on Tuesday night in the season opener. Mohammed Abdulsalam had 11 rebounds for UNC Greensboro. Tyler Maye had 17 points for the Aggies. Marcus Watson added 17 points and eight rebounds. Justin Whatley had eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
